Class DiagnosisTreatment

java.lang.Object
hms.DiagnosisTreatment
public class DiagnosisTreatment extends Object
The DiagnosisTreatment class represents the relationship between a diagnosis and its corresponding treatment plan. It includes details such as diagnosis ID, treatment ID, dates of diagnosis and treatment, and a description.
